				SHANGHAI SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC TECHNOLOGY CO.,LTD. provides you with SUNSEEKER robotic lawn mower intelligent service application products. This software is a service mobile application software based on SUNSEEKER robotic lawn mower. Please read each clause in this agreement carefully. 

				Please read and understand all the rights and restrictions stipulated in the User Agreement (hereinafter referred to as the Agreement) before using the SUNSEEKER lawn mower series products (hereinafter referred to as this product), especially the bold part of the font. If you have any questions about the content of this agreement or the information on the page, please do not proceed to the next step. 

				SHANGHAI SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC TECHNOLOGY CO.,LTD. (hereinafter referred to as SUNSEEKER) respects and will strictly protect the legitimate rights and interests of users (including user privacy, user data, etc.) when using this product from any infringement. 

				This agreement will be legally binding on the user's use of this product, and you have promised and guaranteed that you have the right and ability to enter into this agreement. If you are a person with no capacity for civil conduct or a person with limited capacity for civil conduct, please inform your guardian, and read this agreement and use our services under the guidance of your guardian. Users who start to use this product will be deemed to have accepted this agreement and are voluntarily bound by this agreement. Please carefully read and understand the terms of this agreement, especially the exemption clauses exempting and restricting SUNSEEKER’s liability and the user's rights restrictions (minors should be accompanied by legal guardians when reviewing), if you cannot accept all terms in this agreement, please do not use this product. Your download, installation, use of this software or account acquisition or login will be deemed as acceptance of this agreement, and you agree to be bound by the terms of this agreement. 

				SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC has the right to amend this agreement, and the updated terms of the agreement will be published in this product, effective from the date of publication. After SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC modifies the terms of this agreement, if the user does not accept the modified terms, please stop using the product immediately, and the user will be deemed to have accepted the modified agreement if the user continues to use the product. 

1、Registration and confirmation 

1.1 If you install and use this product, you must register and provide relevant personal information on the registration page. Once you register or use this service, you are deemed to have fully understood and agreed to all the terms under this agreement, including any modifications made by SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC to this agreement. At the same time you must promise and guarantee: 

1.1.1 All registration information you submit must be true and accurate; 

1.1.2 Your use of this product must be legal; 

1.1.3 You can terminate the use of your account at any time by instructions; 

1.1.4 Be sure to read carefully and fully understand the content of each clause. If you do not agree with this statement or any of its content, you should immediately stop the registration process. 

1.2 Be sure to read carefully and fully understand the content of each clause. If you do not agree with this statement or any of its content, you should immediately stop the registration process. 

1.2.1 After you agree to this agreement and the Privacy Policy or register, you are deemed to agree that this product can obtain your information, data, etc., and agree that this product will integrate and use your information and data under the premise of compliance with laws and regulations, in order to provide you with better various service functions or continuous services, create service value by maximizing the use of your data. Please read it carefully during registration. After obtaining your consent, this product will collect subsequent information. This product guarantees that it will not collect information that is prohibited by laws and regulations. Information collected includes: 

1.2.2 When you register as a member, the email address provided is used to help you automatically extract information such as changes to the account binding or managed smart devices; 

1.2.3 The information proactively provided to us when you browse or use SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC 's products or services can help you quickly get after-sales service and devices details management. We can use the information you provide to profile your behavior preferences, etc., so as to provide you with more personalized and convenient services; 

1.2.4 Relevant information recorded in the process of providing you with services, so that you can check the required devices dynamics or related after-sales service progress, etc.; 

1.2.5 When providing after-sales service to you, we will collect your location information and devices status for perfect service, so as to provide you with more perfect and faster service; 

1.2.5 You can actively submit feedback information through our customer service staff or other channels, so that we can understand and evaluate service quality and optimize user experience; 

1.2.6 Collect and store legally obtained information about you from affiliates, business partners, or third-party independent sources; 

1.2.7 The information you provide, SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC will maximize the reasonable business obligations to keep confidential. With your consent, this product will provide you with services such as the information of device’s after-sales service and version upgrades. 

1.3 Your other information 

In order to make it more convenient for you to use this product and improve the security of your use of our services, our server will collect Mac information about your lawn mower device, Bluetooth information that can be obtained by mobile terminals, device location information, third-party account user's name, profile picture and other similar characteristics records. 

2、 User content 

2.1 User content refers to all content generated when the user downloads, publishes or uses this product in other ways (for example: your information, pictures or other content); 

2.2 You are the only person responsible for your user content. After you register, operations and instructions due to your user content are deemed to be made by you. If the account, password and other information is fraudulently used, stolen or used illegally due to your reasons, you shall bear the risks and losses caused by this. At the same time, you will bear the risk of you or any third party being identified due to the disclosure of your user content; 

2.3 You have agreed that your user content is restricted by Article 4; 

2.4 According to the provisions of this agreement, this product will grant you the following non-transferable, non-exclusive licenses: 

2.4.1 Right to use this product; 

2.4.2 The right to download, install, and use this product in all your network communications. 

2.5 Based on the needs of operational and safety, we may suspend or restrict some functions of the software service of this product, or add new functions 

3、 SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC owns all the rights, ownership and interests of this product, including related intellectual property rights. 

