4.1 You cannot license, sell, lease, transfer, distribute or use this product in any form for other commercial purposes; 

4.2 Unless expressly provided by law, you cannot copy, distribute, republish, download, display or post any part of this product in any form or method; 

4.3 You have agreed to upload, publish or o use this product service in other ways. During the use, you will bear all legal responsibilities arising from the risks caused by the following actions: 

4.3.1 Undermining the basic principles established by the Constitution; 

4.3.2 Endangering national security, leaking state secrets, subverting state power, and undermining national unity 

4.3.3 Damaging the reputation or interests of the state; 

4.3.4 Inciting ethnic hatred or discrimination to undermine ethnic solidarity; 

4.3.5 Detrimental to state religious policies, propagating heretical or superstitious ideas; 

4.3.6 Spreading rumors to disturb economic and social order; 

4.3.7 Disseminating obscenity, pornography, force, brutality and terror or crime-abetting; 

4.3.8 Humiliating or defaming others or infringing upon their reputation, privacy and other legitimate rights and interests; 

4.3.9 Other contents as prohibited by laws and administrative regulations. 

4.4 You have agreed not to engage in the following behaviors with this product: 

4.4.1 Upload or publish computer viruses, worms, malicious code, software that deliberately destroys or changes computer systems or data; 

4.4.2 Collect information or data of other users without authorization, such as real names, ID numbers, and mobile phone numbers; 

4.4.3 Disable the client of this software, cause excessive burden on the server or interfere in other ways; 

4.4.4 Try to use or access this product or background server without authorization; 

4.4.5 Interfere with or destroy the use of other users of this product. 

5、 User privacy protection 

				 Privacy Policy is a part of this agreement, you can find it in the Privacy Policy on the previous interface. Please read carefully and understand all the content in the privacy policy. Your use of this product is deemed that you understand and agree to be bound by the privacy policy, otherwise, please do not use this product. 

6、 Modification and termination 

6.1 Modification 

6.1.1 This agreement allows for changes at any time. If there are any substantial changes to this agreement, we will notify you through the official website or announcement of this product. If you continue to use this product after this agreement has been changed, it will be deemed that you agree to be bound by the changed terms; 

6.1.2 SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC reserves the right to modify, reserve or close any service of this product at any time without notice; 

6.1.3 You have agreed that SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC does not need to be liable to you or a third party for modifying, retaining or closing any service of this product. 

6.2 Termination 

6.2.1 This agreement is effective from the date you accept it, and will continue to be effective during your use of this product until terminated in accordance with this agreement; 

6.2.2 Notwithstanding the above provisions, if you use this product earlier than the time you accept this agreement, you hereby know and agree that this agreement will take effect the first time you use this product; 

6.2.3 We may (1) reserve your right to use this product or account on this website in accordance with the provisions of the law; (2) we will terminate this agreement at any time and for any reason, regardless of whether you notify it or not, including the good faith belief that you violated our acceptable use policy or other provisions of this agreement; 

6.2.4 Not limited by the provisions of the preceding paragraph, if the user infringes the intellectual property rights or other legal rights of a third party, SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC reserves the right to terminate this agreement after receiving the notice from the right holder or its agent; 

6.2.5 Once this agreement is terminated, your right to use this product will terminate. You should be aware that the termination of your agreement means that your user content will be deleted from our active database. SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC shall not be liable to you for terminating this agreement, including but not limited to terminating your user account and deleting your user content. 

7、Third Party Information and Services 

7.1 You have known or agreed that our services are based on third-party technical support, such as Apple iOS, Google Android, etc. You already know that this agreement is signed between you and SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC, not between you and the aforementioned third party. SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC is the only person responsible for the content, maintenance, support services, guarantees and litigation arising from this product. You have agreed to comply with and authorize SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC to restrict your conditional use of this product's services; 

7.2 Such third party’s terms and policies shall apply to the User’s use of such third party information and services. 

7.3Your interaction with other users is only the behavior between you and other users, and this product does not assume any legal responsibility for such behavior. You have agreed that this product will not be liable for the results of such interactive behaviors. 

8、Notification 

8.1 The user must provide a valid email address that you frequently use recently in the account of this product. This product is not responsible for the risk that the email address you provided cannot be used or for any reason so that we cannot deliver the notice to you; 

8.2 The announcement notice issued by this product or the email containing such notice sent to you will undoubtedly constitute a valid notice. 

9、Applicable law 

9.1 This agreement is governed by the laws of the People's Republic of China 

9.2 If there is a dispute between the two parties, they should be resolved through friendly negotiation; if the negotiation fails, either party should file a lawsuit in the court where SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC is located. 

10、 Independence 

				Some terms in this agreement cannot be applied for some reason, other terms of this agreement continue to apply and the unapplicable terms will be modified so that they can be applied in accordance with the law. 

11、Entire Agreement 

11.1 This Agreement, including the Privacy Policy, is the final, complete and exclusive agreement between you and this Product regarding matters related to this Product, and supersedes and incorporates any previous discussions and agreements between the Parties regarding such matters, including the previous end user authorization, service terms and privacy policy; 

11.2 The heading for each part is inserted for convenience of reading, and does not imply any legal or contractual obligations; 

11.3 Unless as approved by SUNSEEKER ROBOTIC in writing, you are not allowed to transfer any right or obligation provided in this Agreement. Any attempt of transfer in violation of above provisions shall be invalid. 

12、 Disclaimer 

				If the following situations occur, this product does not assume any legal liability in the event of any of the following: 

12.1 provision of your personal information as required by law or as required by relevant government agencies; 

12.2 disclosure of any personal information due to your own improper use or other reasons; 

12.3 Failure to satisfy Customers' requirements caused by any interruption, blockage, etc. because of hacking, computer virus intrusion, illegal content information, harassment information screening, government control and monitor as well as problems with any other network, technology, communication lines, information security management measures, etc; 

12.4 The Customer's communication line failure caused by the third party such as the operator, technical problems, network, computer failure, system instability and other losses caused by force majeure; 

12.5 The risks associated with the use of this product’s information, procedures, and services that may have anonymous or impersonal information, including threatening, defamatory, offensive, or illegal content; 

12.6 Any psychological, physical, or economic losses caused by interactions with other customers and their deceiving or misleading information. 

13、 Contact information 

				Please contact us if you have any issues regarding our Privacy Policy and User Agreement, including questions on exercising your rights, any enquiries or complaints, opting-out of direct marketing information, or have any questions about the processing of your personal information, please contact us according to the following contact information. If your concerns are not resolved, you have the right to complain to your local authorities, workplace, or local regulatory agency, where you believe a violation occurred. 

				 Adress: Rm.301, 226 Gaoji Ra., SiJing Town, SongJiang District, Shanghai, China 

				Email: Harry@sunseekerpower.cn 

